%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20US%20Army's%20new%20plan%20to%20counter%20Russia%20and%20China%20has%20a%20glaring%20problem%2C%20experts%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20in%20training%20on%20a%2012-mile%20ruck%20march%20at%20Fort%20Moore%2C%20Georgia%20in%20January.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e4c5ef27898f532d64da1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoldiers%20in%20training%20on%20a%2012-mile%20ruck%20march%20at%20Fort%20Moore%2C%20Georgia%20in%20January.%3Cp%3ECapt.%20Stephanie%20Snyder%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army's%20new%20structure%20responds%20to%20drones%20and%20guided%20missiles%20and%20artillery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20Army%20plans%20to%20stand%20up%20new%20units%20at%20a%20time%20its%20recruiting%20is%20struggling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Army%20is%20also%20basing%20its%20plans%20on%20untried%20weapons%2C%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%20warned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20reorganizing%20to%20fight%20against%20major%20powers%20like%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20but%20it%20lacks%20the%20troops%20and%20new%20recruits%20to%20carry%20it%20out%2C%20congressional%20analysts%20contend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202024%20Army%20Force%20Structure%20Transformation%20would%20be%20the%20Army's%20fifth%20major%20reorganization%20since%202003.%20Judging%20by%20details%20laid%20out%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapi.army.mil%2Fe2%2Fc%2Fdownloads%2F2024%2F02%2F27%2F091989c9%2Farmy-white-paper-army-force-structure-transformation.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20white%20paper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20emphasis%20will%20be%20on%20responding%20to%20technological%20changes%20in%20warfare%2C%20such%20as%20the%20threat%20of%20drones%20and%20long-range%20guided%20munitions%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20economize%20on%20scarce%20manpower.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%20may%20be%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20one%20thing%20to%20establish%20the%20authorizations%20for%20new%20and%20existing%20units%20discussed%20in%20the%20Army's%20white%20paper%2C%20yet%20another%20to%20fill%20those%20authorizations%20with%20qualified%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20warns%20a%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrsreports.congress.gov%2Fproduct%2Fpdf%2FR%2FR47985%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%2C%20which%20analyzes%20issues%20for%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20striking%20aspect%20of%20the%20Army's%20plan%20is%20the%20large%20number%20of%20new%20units%2C%20for%20counter-drone%20protection%20as%20well%20as%20air%20and%20missile%20defense.%20These%20units%2C%20assigned%20to%20corps-%20and%20division-level%20formations%2C%20would%20include%20four%20more%20%26quot%3Bindirect%20fire%20protection%20capability%26quot%3B%20battalions%20intended%20to%20shoot%20down%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20artillery%20and%20mortar%20shells.%20In%20addition%2C%20there%20would%20be%20nine%20counter-small%20UAS%20batteries%20tasked%20with%20destroying%20small%20drones%2C%20and%20four%20more%20Maneuver%20Short%20Range%20Air%20Defense%20(M-SHORAD)%20battalions%20to%20stop%20manned%20aircraft%2C%20helicopters%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20would%20help%20flesh%20out%20the%20Army's%20five%20Multi-Domain%20Task%20Forces%2C%20theater-level%20units%20with%20exotic%20capabilities%20such%20as%20hypersonic%20missiles%2C%20cyberwarfare%2C%20jamming%2C%20and%20integrating%20intelligence%20data.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Army%20is%20trying%20to%20address%20a%20recruiting%20crisis%20that%20has%20left%20some%20units%20undermanned.%20The%20transformation%20plan%20would%20reduce%20authorized%20strength%20%E2%80%94%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20soldiers%20allowed%20%E2%80%94%20from%20494%2C000%20to%20470%2C000.%20The%20Army%20currently%20has%20about%20450%2C000%20active-duty%20troops.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20had%20770%2C000%20soldiers%20in%20the%20latter%20stages%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20when%20it%20was%20structured%20to%20counter%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Army%20will%20shrink%20excess%2C%20largely%20unmanned%20'hollow'%20force%20structure%20and%20build%20new%20formations%20equipped%20with%20new%20capabilities%20needed%20for%20large%20scale%20combat%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Army%20white%20paper%20explained.%20This%20would%20include%203%2C000%20fewer%20authorized%20special%20operations%20forces%20personnel.%20Some%20functions%20will%20also%20be%20consolidated%2C%20such%20as%20reassigning%20engineers%20from%20brigade%20combat%20teams%20to%20divisions%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20fewer%20engineer%20slots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20with%20consolidation%20and%20a%20boost%20to%20recruitment%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-army%2F2024%2F01%2F02%2Farmy-to-open-applications-for-new-recruiting-warrant-officer-field%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enew%20warrant%20officers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20specialize%20in%20recruiting%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Army%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20find%20enough%20personnel%20to%20fill%20out%20its%20existing%20units%20and%20create%20new%20air%20defense%20formations.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20Army%20came%20up%2010%2C000%20short%20in%20its%20quest%20for%2065%2C000%20new%20recruits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20past%20recruiting%20shortfalls%20and%20preliminary%20FY2024%20recruiting%20data%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20predict%20if%20the%20Army%20will%20be%20able%20rectify%20its%20recruiting%20challenges%20in%20the%20near%20and%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20CRS%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Army%20may%20also%20be%20focusing%20too%20much%20on%20cutting-edge%20%26quot%3Bsoft%26quot%3B%20technologies%20rather%20than%20old-fashioned%20kinetic%20weapons%20that%20have%20proven%20quite%20relevant%20and%20lethal%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Army%20white%20paper%20appears%20to%20address%20technology-based%2C%20non-kinetic%20space%20and%20cyber%20effects%2C%20long-range%20precision%20fires%2C%20and%20force%20protection%20more%20than%20it%20does%20conventional%20close-combat%20force%20capabilities%2C%20Army%20Special%20Operations%20Forces%20capabilities%2C%20and%20Security%20Force%20Assistance%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%205-kilowatt%20laser%20sits%20on%20a%20Stryker%20armored%20vehicle%20in%202017.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e3b2eb4abc992e8c808cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%205-kilowatt%20laser%20sits%20on%20a%20Stryker%20armored%20vehicle%20in%202017.%3Cp%3EMonica%20K.%20Guthrie%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Army%20is%20also%20basing%20its%20plans%20on%20untried%20weapons%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Long-Range%20Hypersonic%20Missile%20and%20air%20defense%20lasers.%20%26quot%3BSome%20units%2C%20such%20as%20LRHW%20batteries%20and%20Directed%20Energy%20(DE)%20SHORAD%20units%2C%20do%20not%20have%20mature%20weapons%20and%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20CRS%20warned.%20Nor%20does%20the%20Army%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Congress%20%E2%80%94%20have%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20the%20reorganization%20would%20cost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInevitably%2C%20there%20will%20also%20be%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20yet%20another%20Army%20metamorphosis.%20In%202003%2C%20the%20Army%20switched%20from%20a%20Cold%20War%20force%20structure%20of%20heavy%20mechanized%20divisions%2C%20to%20smaller%2C%20lighter%20brigades%20more%20suitable%20for%20counterinsurgency.%20Now%2C%20the%20Army%20has%20gone%20full%20circle%20as%20it%20reconfigures%20for%20Cold%20War-style%20mechanized%20conflict%20against%20big%20opponents%20like%20Russia%20and%20China.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20must%20also%20incorporate%20new%20technologies%20such%20as%20drones%20and%20long-range%20artillery%2C%20which%20have%20demonstrated%20their%20power%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reorganization%20does%20address%20some%20of%20the%20Army's%20problems%2C%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20units%C2%A0are%20appropriate%20for%20a%C2%A0great%20power%20conflict.%C2%A0China%20and%20Russia%20have%20much%20stronger%20air%20and%20missile%20forces%20than%20the%20regional%C2%A0opponents%20the%20army%20has%20faced%20for%20the%20last%20generation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECreating%20units%20armed%20with%20hypersonic%20missiles%20also%20makes%20sense%2C%20especially%20since%20Russia%20and%20the%20US%20withdrew%20in%202019%20from%20the%20Intermediate-Range%20Nuclear%20Forces%20treaty%2C%20signed%20in%201987%20to%20curb%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20other%20medium-range%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20long-range%20fires%20are%20an%20opportunity%20that%20has%20opened%20up%20with%20the%20end%20of%20the%20INF%2C%26quot%3B%20Cancian%20said.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20reorganization%20doesn't%20address%20the%20real%20issue.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Army's%20major%20problem%20is%20that%20it%20is%20too%20small%20overall%20to%20meet%20all%20of%20its%20likely%20peacetime%20and%20wartime%20commitments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cancian.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-armys-new-plan-russia-china-glaring-problem-crs-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715418001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-armys-new-plan-russia-china-glaring-problem-crs-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Army%20is%20reorganizing%20to%20respond%20to%20rising%20threats%2C%20but%20standing%20up%20new%20units%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20bodybuilder%20ditched%20his%20low-carb%20diet%20and%20started%20eating%20potatoes%206%20times%20a%20day.%20He%20got%20in%20the%20best%20shape%20of%20his%20life.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bodybuilder%20Mark%20Taylor%20surrounded%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20sweet%20potatoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2e6a9686a6f37bfe502f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%2