a%20lot%20of%20his%20later-in-life%20success%20comes%20down%20to%20potatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20shock%20those%20who%20have%20been%20led%20to%20believe%20that%20carbs%20are%20the%20enemy%20of%20fat%20loss.%20The%20anti-carb%20movement%20has%20been%20around%20in%20various%20guises%20for%20decades.%20The%20low-carb%20Atkins%20diet%20was%20popular%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20high-fat%2C%20low-carb%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-ways-keto-ruined-my-relationship-with-food-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eketo%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20gained%20traction%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20and%20now%20there%20is%20increasing%20fear-mongering%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-weight-loss-12-pounds-spiking-increasing-blood-sugar-levels-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20sugar%20%26quot%3Bspikes%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20caused%20by%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20eating%20carbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20Taylor%20found%2C%20carbs%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20our%20diets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-carbs-not-better-than-brown-health-weight-loss-dietitians-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earen't%20inherently%20fattening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20muscle%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Taylor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e39afb4abc992e8c804f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Taylor%20(center)%20competing%20in%20Mr%20Universe.%3Cp%3EMark%20Taylor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204adb260-974c-476e-ae3b-06b12a10399d%5C%22%3ECarbs%20help%20replenish%20energy%20stores%20in%20our%20muscles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20denying%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid