ity%20to%20conduct%20counter-small%20UAS%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20but%20the%20US%20military%20isn't%20there%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20fall%2C%20the%20Army%20launched%20another%20drone%20initiative%3A%20the%20Joint%20C-sUAS%20University.%20In%20Oklahoma's%20Fort%20Sill%2C%20the%20JCU%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-shoot-balloons-learn-to-defeat-dangerous-drone-threat-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsolidates%20counter-drone%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20service%20members%20across%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Marine%20Corps%20Sgt.%20Paul%20Butcher%2C%20an%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20technician%20with%20Special%20Purpose%20Marine%20Air-Ground%20Task%20Force-Crisis%20Response-Central%20Command%2C%20flies%20a%20DJI%20Mavic%20Pro%20Drone%20while%20forward%20deployed%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20on%20May%2025%2C%202017.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e320ff27898f532d6195a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20Sgt.%20Paul%20Butcher%2C%20an%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20technician%20with%20Special%20Purpose%20Marine%20Air-Ground%20Task%20Force-Crisis%20Response-Central%20Command%2C%20flies%20a%20DJI%20Mavic%20Pro%20Drone%20while%20forward%20deployed%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20on%20May%2025%2C%202017.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Cpl.%20Shellie%20Hall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20there%20spend%20several%20weeks%20learning%20how%20to%20identify%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20defeat%20small%20drones.%20The%20training%20involves%20working%20with%20early-warning%20radars%20to%20detect%20the%20aircraft%20and%20using%20handheld%20devices%2C%20including%20electronic-warfare%20and%20smart-shooting%20systems%2C%20to%20neutralize%20the%20unmanned%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETr