2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-hamas-rafah-gaza_6549946.jpg%3F20240511075738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-orders-residents-from-more-areas-of-rafah-to-evacuate-13133286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20has%20called%20on%20residents%20from%20more%20areas%20of%20Rafah%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20evacuate%20and%20head%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bexpanded%20humanitarian%20area%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20ramp%20up%20its%20military%20assault.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-orders-residents-from-more-areas-of-rafah-to-evacuate-13133286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-orders-residents-from-more-areas-of-rafah-to-evacuate-13133286%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-orders-residents-from-more-areas-of-rafah-to-evacuate-13133286%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20won't%20win%2050%20LS%20seats%2C%20will%20not%20get%20Oppn%20party%20status%2C%20says%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715409581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1715056108-0565.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-won-t-win-50-ls-seats-will-not-get-oppn-party-status-says-pm-124051100176_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20also%20asserted%20that%20his%20government%20ended%20500%20years%20of%20people's%20wait%20by%20building%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-won-t-win-50-ls-seats-will-not-get-oppn-party-status-says-pm-124051100176_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-won-t-win-50-ls-seats-will-not-get-oppn-party-status-says-pm-124051100176_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fcongress-won-t-win-50-ls-seats-will-not-get-oppn-party-status-says-pm-124051100176_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Elections%20And%20Atom%20Bombs%20Share%20Umbilical%20Technological%20Connect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20elections%20and%20atom%20bombs%20have%20an%20umbilical%20connect.%20The%20same%20facilities%20that%20make%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20also%20helped%20made%20the%20bombs%20in%20Pokhran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20celebrates%20National%20Technology%20Day%20on%20May%2011.%20On%20this%20day%2026%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20sands%20below%20the%20Thar%20desert%20shook%2C%20but%20did%20not%20leak%20radiation%20as%20India%20detonated%20three%20nuclear%20bombs%20in%20Pokhran%20on%20May%2011%2C%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20India%20is%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20general%20election%20with%20nearly%20a%20billion%20people%20eligible%20to%20cast%20their%20votes.%20It%20is%20not%20widely%20known%20that%20it%20is%20the%20same%20institutions%20that%20powered%20the%20nuclear%20explosions%20in%201974%20and%201998%2C%20which%20today%20help%20empower%20the%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20since%20all%20the%20EVMs%20are%20made%20in%20highly%20secure%20facilities%20of%20the%20same%20institutions%20that%20helped%20India%20become%20a%20nuclear%20weapons%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20elections%20today%20are%20the%20most%20secure%20and%20advanced%2C%20since%20the%20same%20departments%20who%20helped%20make%20India's%20atom%20bombs%20make%20the%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%205.5%20million%20EVM's%20have%20been%20deployed%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20has%20said%20in%20what%20is%20the%20world's%20single-largest%20democratic%20exercise.%20Each%20EVM%20can%20record%20up%20to%202%2C000%20votes%20and%20up%20to%20384%20candidates%20can%20be%20accommodated%20in%20each%20EVM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20EVM's%20have%20been%20made%20at%20two%20highly%20secure%20facilities%20-%20the%20Electronic%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20(ECIL)%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20facility%20that%20comes%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Electronic%20Limited%20(BEL)%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20an%20institution%20under%20the%20Defence%20Ministry.%20Both%20these%20facilities%20help%20make%20some%20of%20the%20most%20rugged%20and%20top%20secret%20hardware%20used%20by%20India's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fpokhran-2-nuclear-weapons-testing_650x400_81526020399.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECIL%20helps%20make%20much%20of%20the%20electronics%20that%20goes%20into%20making%20India's%20atomic%20power%20plants.%20It%20was%20deeply%20involved%20in%20fabricating%20the%20sophisticated%20and%20miniaturised%20electronics%20that%20went%20into%20India's%20fission%20and%20fusion%20bombs.%20ECIL%20also%20makes%20jam-proof%20and%20hacking%20secure%20communications%20devices%20for%20India's%20military%2C%20and%20so%20making%20EVMs%20the%20standalone%20calculator-like%20devices%20that%20are%20unconnected%20to%20any%20other%20device%20through%20Wi-Fi%20or%20Bluetooth%20is%20almost%20child's%20play%20for%20the%20scientists%20at%20ECIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBEL%20is%20India's%20top%20facility%20making%20the%20most%20advanced%20electronics%20that%20goes%20into%20India's%20missile%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20the%20intercontinental-range%20ballistic%20missile%20Agni-5%2C%20nuclear-powered%20submarines%2C%20Tejas%20fighter%20jets%2C%20spy%20satellites%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20aircraft%20carriers%20On%20the%20side%2C%20BEL%20makes%20tamper-%20and%20hack-proof%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20the%20lifespan%20of%20an%20EVM%20is%2015%20years%20and%20the%20control%20unit%20costs%20Rs%209%2C812%3B%20the%20balloting%20unit%20costs%20Rs%207%2C991%20and%20the%20voter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20costs%20Rs%2016%2C132.%20So%20the%20whole%20unit%20costs%20about%20Rs%2033%2C935.%20The%20ECI%20spent%20Rs%203%2C960.10%20crore%20between%2C%202021%20and%202023%20to%20buy%20the%20latest%20model%20called%20%26quot%3BM3%20EVMs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EVMs%20are%20manufactured%20in%20secure%20assembly%20lines%20at%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20and%20all%20the%20movement%20is%20video%20recorded.%20The%20only%20component%20that%20is%20imported%20for%20the%20EVMs%20is%20the%20chip%2C%20which%20is%20sourced%20from%20European%20foundries%20and%20trusted%20sources.%20This%20import%20is%20still%20being%20done%20since%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20for%20silicon%20chips.%20Once%20the%20India%20Semi-Conductor%20Mission%20takes%20off%2C%20even%20this%20import%20of%20chips%20may%20come%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%202019%2C%20the%20EC%20has%20deployed%20only%20the%20M3%20EVMs%2C%20which%20are%20the%20most%20advanced%20and%20all%20the%20earlier%20models%20M1%20and%20M2%20have%20been%20discarded%20for%20good.%20According%20to%20EC%2C%20the%20M3%20models%20have%20a%20unique%20and%20new%20self-diagnostic%20feature%20and%20if%20it%20is%20tampered%20with%2C%20the%20machine%20shuts%20down%20and%20becomes%20inoperable.%20Once%20it%20goes%20into%20this%20safety%20mode%2C%20only%20the%20original%20manufacturer%20can%20restore%20it%2C%20so%20experts%20who%20oversee%20EVMs%20say%20they%20are%20literally%20tamper-proof%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20EC%20show%20that%20till%20date%20a%20total%20of%20about%20340%20crore%20votes%20have%20been%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20in%20India%20during%20the%20last%20four%20consecutive%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20and%20in%20132%20different%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20EC%20says%20%26quot%3Bno%20incident%20of%20EVM%20tampering%20has%20ever%20been%20found%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20EVMs%20just%20can't%20be%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20said.%20Even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20affirmed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20are%20best%20in%20their%20class%20of%20institutions%20that%20make%20components%20used%20to%20secure%20India's%20borders.%20That%20they%20also%20help%20secure%20India's%20democracy%20and%20freedom%20is%20like%20a%20small%20side%20activity.%20For%20them%2C%20making%20atom%20bombs%20and%20missiles%20is%20bread%20and%20butter%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20EVMs%20is%20just%20the%20jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715409360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fjtvegvdo_election-2022-election-generic-evm-generic-ani-650_625x300_20_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-elections-and-atom-bombs-share-umbilical-technological-connect-5638210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20elections%20and%20atom%20bombs%20have%20an%20umbilical%20connect%2C%20the%20same%20facilities%20which%20make%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM's)%20also%20helped%20make%20the%20bombs%20at%20Pokhran.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-elections-and-atom-bombs-share-umbilical-technological-connect-5638210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-elections-and-atom-bombs-share-umbilical-technological-connect-5638210%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-elections-and-atom-bombs-share-umbilical-technological-co