t%20to%20make%20an%20attempt%20to%20win%20back%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Amethi%20and%20contesting%20from%20the%20relatively%20safe%20seat%20of%20Raebareli.%C2%A0His%20mother%20and%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20held%20the%20Raebareli%20constituency%20since%202004%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Inheritance%20Tax%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20row%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-quits-congress-post-after-huge-row-over-his-racist-remarks-5618579%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Pitroda's%20comment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20inheritance%20tax%20in%20the%20US%20was%20an%20interesting%20law%20and%20could%20contain%20issues%20that%20people%20can%20debate.%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20to%20have%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20against%20the%20inheritance%20tax.%20I%20just%20think%20it's%20unfair%20to%20have%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%20A%20person%20tries%20to%20earn%20for%20his%20children%20his%20whole%20life%20and%20then%20you%20half%20of%20it.%20It%20would%20be%20good%20for%20other%20countries%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20right%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20who%20was%20an%20advisor%20to%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20has%20been%20closely%20associated%20with%20his%20son%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20accompanying%20him%20during%20his%20foreign%20visits%2C%20had%20last%20month%20stoked%20a%20debate%20over%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20planning%20a%20redistribution%20of%20wealth%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20after%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20America%2C%20there%20is%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%20If%20one%20has%20100%20million%20USD%2