%20advocate%20Christopher%20Anthony's%20petition%20to%20register%20a%20case%20against%20Ms%20Khan%20as%20well%20as%20the%20book's%20sellers.%20The%20court%20has%20sought%20an%20answer%20from%20the%20actor%20on%20why%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bbible%26quot%3B%20was%20used%20in%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotices%20have%20also%20been%20issued%20to%20the%20sellers%20of%20the%20books%20after%20Mr%20Anthony%20demanded%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20book's%20sale%20in%20his%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Anthony%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20from%20Jabalpur%2C%20has%20alleged%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bbible%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20book's%20title%20is%20hurtful%20to%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Christian%20community.%20%26quot%3BBible%20is%20the%20holy%20book%20of%20Christianity%20all%20over%20the%20world%20and%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20compare%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan's%20pregnancy%20with%20the%20Bible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Anthony%20says%20the%20actor%20used%20the%20word%20to%20gain%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20publicity%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%2C%20published%20in%202021%2C%20chronicles%20the%2043-year-old%20actor's%20pregnancy%20journey%20and%20provides%20tips%20for%20expecting%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20had%20first%20approached%20the%20police%20to%20register%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20against%20the%20actor%20but%20when%20they%20refused%20to%20file%20a%20case%2C%20he%20moved%20a%20lower%20court%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20request%20was%20rejected%20after%20the%20court%20said%20his%20petition%20failed%20to%20establish%20how%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bbible%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20title%20was%20offensive.%20He%20then%20moved%20the%20Additional%20Sessions%20Court%20which%20dismissed%20his%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan's%20Pregnancy%20Bible%3A%20The%20Ultimate%20Manual%20for%20Moms-To-Be%26quot%3B%20includes%20tips%20from%20experts%20on%20diet%2C%20fitness%2C%20self-care%20and%20nursery%20preparation%20for%20expecting%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Sanjeev%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715406720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvhgjku2_kareena_625x300_30_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkareena-kapoor-gets-court-notice-for-using-bible-in-pregnancy-book-title-5638084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Bollywood%20actor%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20on%20a%20petition%20against%20her%20new%20pregnancy%20memoir%20%26quot%3BKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan's%20Pregnancy%20Bible.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkareena-kapoor-gets-court-notice-for-using-bible-in-pregnancy-book-title-5638084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkareena-kapoor-gets-court-notice-for-using-bible-in-pregnancy-book-title-5638084%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkareena-kapoor-gets-court-notice-for-using-bible-in-pregnancy-book-title-5638084%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%205%20Years%2C%20We%20Will...%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20Chief's%20Big%20Promise%20For%20'Make%20In%20India'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20today%20said%20that%20his%20party%20resolves%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20from%2014%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20about%20making%20(manufacturing)%20in%20India%20on%20his%20official%20X%20handle%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20resolves%20to%20make%20India%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20from%2014%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%205%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELauding%20the%20Congress's%20regime%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20claimed%20that%20the%20nation's%20manufacturing%20share%20of%20GDP%20was%20higher%20compared%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20thus%20no%20surprise%20that%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20India's%20manufacturing%20share%20of%20GDP%20has%20been%20higher%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20(2014-24)%2C%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20has%20stagnated%20at%20just%2014%25%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20India%20the%20manufacturing%20powerhouse%20that%20produces%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20itself%20and%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party's%20immediate%20objective%20will%20be%20to%20restore%20a%20healthy%2C%20fearless%20and%20trustworthy%20climate%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20party's%20goal%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%201991%20abolished%20industrial%20licensing%20and%20controls.%20%26quot%3BThe%20independent%20regulatory%20regime%20that%20was%20put%20in%20place%20has%20deteriorated%20into%20a%20system%20of%20overt%20and%20covert%20controls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20current%20rules%20and%20regulations%20and%20repeal%20or%20amend%20them%20in%20order%20to%20restore%20freedom%20to%20industry%2C%20business%20and%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20Congress'%20ambition%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20aim%20for%20India%20to%20attain%20a%20position%20of%20leadership%20in%20multiple%20industries%20such%20as%20steel%2C%20metals%2C%20garments%20and%20textiles%2C%20cement%2C%20automobiles%2C%20electronic%20goods%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20engineering%20goods%2C%20petroleum%20products%2C%20chemicals%2C%20and%20mining%20rare%20earth%20and%20critical%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20forward%20RBI's%20data%20on%20stalled%20projects%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20Congress%20will%20revive%20those%20projects%20by%20taking%20the%20help%20of%20the%20private%20sector.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20RBI%2C%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20large%20central%20government%20projects%20have%20been%20stalled%20or%20delayed%20and%20costs%20have%20risen%20by%20nearly%205%20lakh%20crores.%20Congress%20will%20address%20the%20problem%20in%20a%20mission%20mode%20and%20find%20ways%20and%20means%20to%20revive%20the%20stalled%20projects%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20private%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrowing%20light%20on%20the%20Congress%20approach%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20reform%20the%20production%20linked%20incentives%20(PLI)%20scheme%20to%20target%20specific%20sectors%20that%20can%20create%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20by%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20top%205%20producers%20in%20the%20world%20in%20that%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20also%20mentioned%20about%20introducing%20an%20employment-linked%20incentive%20scheme.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20introduce%20a%20new%20employment-linked%20incentive%20(ELI)%20Scheme%20for%20corporates%20to%20win%20tax%20credits%20for%20additional%20hiring%20against%20regular%2C%20quality%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20party's%20opposition%20to%20monopolies%20and%20oligopolies%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20create%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20businesses.%20We%20are%20opposed%20to%20monopolies%20and%20oligopolies.%20We%20will%20strengthen%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20to%20ensure%20that%20India%20will%20be%20an%20open%20and%20competitive%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20President%20also%20talked%20about%20strengthening%20AI%20and%20robotics%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20encourage%20and%20support%20the%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20robotics%2C%20etc.%20which%20will%20create%20new%20and%20frontline%20jobs.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20more%20job%20opportunities%20in%20sectors%20that%20use%20conventional%20technology.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715406480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F10bq500g_mallikarjun-kharge-pm-narendra-modi_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-5-years-we-will-congress-chiefs-big-promise-for-make-in-india-5637934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20today%20said%20that%20his%20party%20resolves%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20from%2014%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-5-years-we-will-congress-chiefs-big-promise-for-make-in-india-5637934%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-5-years-we-will-congress-chiefs-big-promise-for-make-in-india-5637934%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-5-years-we-will-congress-chiefs-big-promi