y%20to%20do%20so%20anytime%20soon%2C%20is%20taking%20notice.%20In%20his%20latest%20earnings%20report%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-blames-hybrids-for-lower-sales-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblamed%20demand%20for%20hybrid%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20depressing%20global%20EV%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20EV%20adoption%20rate%20globally%20is%20under%20pressure%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20auto%20manufacturers%20are%20pulling%20back%20on%20EVs%20and%20pursuing%20plug-in%20hybrids%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20an%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20strategy%2C%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20will%20ultimately%20dominate%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20hybrid%20owners%2C%20experts%20and%20industry%20execs%20to%20discover%20why%20hybrids%20are%20gaining%20popularity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af74f03e-f0cb-4d4f-8a61-2ca0833223f8%5C%22%3ELack%20of%20affordable%20EVs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20O'Brien%2C%20who%20teaches%20auto%20tech%20at%20Jefferson%20Community%20College%20in%20Kentucky%2C%20took%20delivery%20of%20a%20hybrid%202024%20Ford%20Maverick%20in%20February%2C%20and%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20with%20his%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20hybrid%20perfectly%20balanced%20excellent%20fuel%20economy%20with%20a%20reduced%20environmental%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20very%20quiet%2C%20very%20smooth%2C%20and%20more%20than%20double%20the%20fuel%20economy%20of%20my%20previous%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Brien%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20believes%20EVs%20are%20the%20future%2C%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20affordable%20options%20meant%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20hybrid%20instead%20for%20his%20next%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20barrier%20for%20me%20personally%20is%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20new%20EV%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20just%20aren't%20many%20EV%20options%20yet%20that%20regular%20people%20(as%20opposed%20to%20rich%20people)%20can%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20affordable%20EVs%20has%20been%20cited%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectrc-vehicle-demand-problem-affordability-expense-price-cost-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20why%20drivers%20are%20reluctant%20to%20go%20electric%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHybrids%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20affordable%20than%20pure%20EVs%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20reaping%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20paid%20%2442%2C500%20for%20hybrids%20in%20November%202023%20on%20average%20compared%20with%20%2460%2C500%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20%2447%2C500%20for%20gas%20cars%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Edmunds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fbusiness%2Fhybrid-cars-electric-vehicles.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20additional%20costs%20associated%20with%20fully%20electric%20vehicles%20is%20definitely%20higher%20than%20hybrids%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Singer%2C%20a%20senior%20transportation%20analyst%20at%20the%20National%20Renewable%20Energy%20Laboratory%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20hybrid%20electric%20vehicles%20now%20are%20not%20far%20off%20from%20their%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20alternatives.%20So%20I%20think%20that%20the%20lower%20incremental%20costs%20associated%20with%20hybrids%20at%20this%20point%20are%20driving%20some%20interest%20towards%20hybrid%20versus%20fully%20electric%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299ed0829-d858-4969-b375-e264f3970cfd%5C%22%3ESoaring