Business%20Insider%20that%20customers%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20a%20choice%20between%20hybrids%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20combustion%20engines%2C%20and%20that%20Toyota%20was%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20having%20options%20in%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20every%20segment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20hybrids%20now%20that%20there's%20no%20compromises%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20super%20efficient%2C%20they're%20powerful%2C%20the%20styling%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToyota%20is%20expecting%20around%2040%25%20of%20its%20total%20US%20sales%20to%20be%20in%20hybrids%20this%20year%2C%20Buchanan%20said%2C%20with%20sales%20of%20partially%20and%20fully%20electrified%20vehicles%20up%2070%25%20in%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20relative%20affordability%20of%20hybrids%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%26quot%3B%20factor%20swaying%20consumers%20towards%20hybrids%2C%20especially%20as%20interest%20rates%20have%20risen%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20but%20added%20that%20lingering%20concerns%20over%20charging%20were%20also%20putting%20customers%20off%20from%20going%20fully%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20doubt%20that%20for%20some%20people%20a%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchanan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20not%20enough%20public%20charging%20out%20there%20to%20make%20all%20customers%20comfortable%20with%20it%2C%20and%20I%20do%20think%20that%20probably%20is%20driving%20more%20customers%20back%20towards%20hybrids%20and%20plug-in%20hybrids%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESinger%20agreed%2C%20pointing%20to%20affordability%20and%20charging%20as%20the%20biggest%20factors%20swaying%20consumers%20from%20taking%20the%20plunge%20and%20buying%20a%20pure%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20the%20two%20issues%20that%20are%20proving%20the%20biggest%20barriers%20to%20adoption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20neither%20barrier%20an%20issue%20for%20hybrids%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20hybrid%20boom%20is%20unlikely%20to%20die%20down%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrids-sales-booming-why-drivers-are-buying-them-over-evs-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715400481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634c49710dfcda4096653c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrids-sales-booming-why-drivers-are-buying-them-over-evs-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sales%20of%20partially%20battery-powered%20vehicles%2C%20once%20ridiculed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bphase%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20are%20rocketing%20even%20as%20EVs%20stutter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40insider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrids-sales-booming-why-drivers-are-buying-them-over-evs-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20Says%20Trump%20Should%20Have%20Injected%20%26quot%3BSome%26quot%3B%20Bleach%20During%20Pandemic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20joked%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20wished%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20injected%20himself%20with%20a%20little%20bleach%2C%20resurrecting%20one%20of%20Trump's%20more%20head-scratching%20moments%20from%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20at%20a%20fundraising%20event%20south%20of%20San%20Francisco%20for%20his%20re-election%20campaign%2C%20said%20the%20presidency%20of%20his%20Republican%20opponent%20was%20chaotic%20and%20that%20voters%20should%20keep%20that%20in%20mind.%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20close%20contest%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRememb