ww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-david-depape-the-suspected-pelosi-attacker-reports-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20DePape%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20facing%20a%20possible%2040-year%20sentence%20for%20his%202022%20attack%20on%20Paul%20Pelosi%2C%20husband%20of%20Rep.%20Nancy%20Pelosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sentencing%20memo%20filed%20Friday%20and%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20prosecutors%20requested%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24658434-sentencing-memo-against-david-depape-in-attack-of-paul-pelosi%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrorism%20enhancement%3C%2Fa%3E%20be%20added%20to%20DePape's%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDePape%20still%20faces%20additional%20charges%20related%20to%20the%20attack%2C%20including%20attempted%20murder%2C%20that%20carry%20a%20potential%20sentence%20of%2013%20years%20to%20life%20in%20prison.%20He%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Pelosi%20suffered%20two%20skull%20fractures%20that%20required%20surgery%20to%20fix%20after%20DePape%20struck%20him%20in%20the%20head%20with%20a%20hammer%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20occurred%20after%20DePape%20broke%20into%20Pelosi's%20San%20Francisco%20home%2C%20seeking%20to%20kidnap%20then-Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20and%20break%20her%20kneecaps%20to%20teach%20her%20that%20her%20%26quot%3Blies%20and%20corruption%20had%20a%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-depape-convicted-nancy-pelosi-husband-attack-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDePape%20was%20found%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20attack%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20November%20after%20about%20eight%20hours%20of%20jury%20deliberation.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHis%20sentencing%20is%20set%20for%20May%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the