%2Fgoa-construction-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20a%20construction%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20start%20teaching%20kids%20of%20the%20workers%20for%20free%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20their%20efforts%20was%20good%2C%20so%20the%20group%20divided%20their%20efforts%20and%20started%20to%20teach%20in%20three%20different%20locations%20in%20Vadodara.%20%EF%BF%BDWithin%20some%20months%2C%20from%20a%20dozen%20kids%2C%20we%20went%20to%20teaching%20hundreds.%20But%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20every%20six%20months%2C%20these%20workers%20would%20move%20and%20hence%20the%20kids%20would%20be%20left%20with%20no%20education%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20students%EF%BF%BD%20mothers%20who%20requested%20Juin%20to%20take%20her%20child%20under%20her%20wing%20and%20provide%20education%20as%20they%20were%20to%20migrate%20once%20more.%20Inspired%20by%20it%2C%20in%202014%2C%20Juin%20decided%20to%20resign%20from%20her%20job%20and%20dedicate%20herself%20to%20assisting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F100208%2Fsnehlata-hooda-teaching-underprivileged-children-in-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20children.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDThis%20was%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20hostel%20was%20born.%20A%20very%20kind%20philanthropist%20from%20the%20city%20helped%20us%20to%20get%20a%20property%20for%20rent%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDThe%20free%20residential%20school%20operates%2C%20unlike%20traditional%20institutions%2C%20employing%20a%20unique%20educational%20model%2C%EF%BF%BD%20Juin%20explains.%20%EF%BF%BDGiven%20the%20diverse%20backgrounds%20of%20our%20students%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20commence%20their%20education%20later%20in%20life%2C%20we%EF%BF%BDve%20adopted%20a%20levelled%20system%20of%20instruction.%20In%20our%20approach%2C%20a%20student%EF%BF%BDs%20level%20in%20a%20particular%20subject%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20proficiency%20rather%20than%20their%20age%2C%20ensuring%20no%20one%20feels%20misplaced%20or%20ashamed%20for%20joining%20later.%EF%BF%BD%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDWe%20also%20prioritise%20sports%20and%20project-based%20activities%2C%20offering%20opportunities%20for%20learning%20beyond%20the%20conventional%20curriculum%2C%20such%20as%20painting%2C%20judo%2C%20and%20karate%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20how%20a%20student%20is%20assigned%20a%20particular%20lever%20and%20how%20they%20navigate%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDWhen%20a%20child%20joins%20Pathshala%2C%20we%20assess%20their%20current%20knowledge%20and%20comprehension%20abilities%20in%20languages%20and%20mathematics.%20Based%20on%20this%20evaluation%2C%20we%20place%20them%20in%20appropriate%20levels%20corresponding%20to%20their%20proficiency.%20Consequently%2C%20each%20child%20studies%20at%20different%20levels%20for%20various%20subjects.%20Upon%20completion%20of%20Level%205%2C%20a%20student%20becomes%20equivalent%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20sit%20for%20Class%208%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Class%208%20to%2012%2C%20the%20school%20adheres%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%20syllabus%2C%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20take%20psychometric%20tests%20to%20discover%20their%20career%20inclinations%2C%20guiding%20their%20subject%20choices%20when%20they%20enter%20Class%208.%20This%20personalised%20method%20ensures%20their%20interests%20and%20strengths%20are%20considered.%20Alongside%20languages%20and%20math%2C%20students%20explore%20diverse%20subjects%20through%20practical%20experiences%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDFor%20instance%2C%20recently%2C%20the%20students%20completed%20a%20board%20game%20project%20where%20they%20designed%20and%20created%20their%20own%20board%20games%2C%20complete%20with%20unique%20rules.%20Students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi