0their%20proficiency%20in%20each%20subject.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20also%20informs%20that%20they%20have%20implemented%20Government%20schemes%20%EF%BF%BDUdyam%EF%BF%BD%20for%20skill%20development%20training%20and%20%EF%BF%BDUnnati%EF%BF%BD%20for%20hands-on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311132%2Fmother-daughter-sustainable-lifestyle-brand-helps-homemakers-earn-bags-shark-tank-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneurial%20training.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDOur%20policy%20is%20to%20support%20them%20until%20they%20achieve%20economic%20independence.%20Pathshala%20is%20fundamentally%20a%20value-based%20institution%2C%20dedicated%20to%20nurturing%20children%EF%BF%BDs%20happiness%20in%20life%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESejal%20Verma%20(21)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20education%20and%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20shares%2C%20%EF%BF%BDI%EF%BF%BDm%20currently%20working%20part-time%20and%20earning%20enough%20to%20support%20myself.%20I%EF%BF%BDm%20also%20pursuing%20a%20course%20at%20ITI%20Vadodara.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20this%20would%20have%20been%20possible%20if%20I%20hadn%EF%BF%BDt%20gained%20admission%20to%20Pathshala%20on%20time.%20I%20had%20passed%20my%20Class%208%20exam%20from%20a%20Government%20school%20but%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20read%20the%20alphabet!%EF%BF%BD%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDIn%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20restarted%20my%20education%20at%20Pathshala.%20Once%20I%20completed%20my%20boards%2C%20they%20helped%20me%20get%20admitted%20into%20ITI%2C%20and%20I%20still%20visit%20the%20hostel.%20It%20feels%20like%20home%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20visiting%20the%20children%20on%20various%20occasions%20like%20festivals%20and%20school%20functions%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%EF%BF%BDWe%20rely%20on%20t